      "raw_text": "The council last night granted\nfranchises to the Inland Empire\nsystem for eastern and southern\nextensions and \"Y's\" over Mayor\nMoore's veto. The only council\nman not favor ing passage was B.\nr. Ostrander.\n\n\nThe city is to receive a revenue\nof two mills per car mile. Mayor\nMoore held this too small, but was\nwilling to agree on demanding 20\nrevenue to the city for five years\nif at the end of that time the, city\ncould get reasonable compensa\nton."
